{
  "stem": "935.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And by the time the day was over, I had a treasure chest in front of me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Everybody brought-- everybody brought stuff.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "My girlfriend, Toni, brought me coins, a lot of foreign coins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Too heavy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I couldn't carry it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And my beloved Margit brought-- said I should bring-- yeah, I should take her guitar, because a girl with a guitar would never be stopped.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I don't know why she thought.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "She said I could either hawk it, you know, get money for it, or I could sing something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Anyway, I got this, and my mother kept running to the post office saying that the papers hadn't come.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I left on the 2nd of May, 1943, on a very beautiful day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I was supposed to meet this Harry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I talked to him on the phone, only Harry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "He had my prescription for a fake ID over the phone-- my height, coloring, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I was supposed to be a student living, visiting my grandmother over the weekend.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Only one little suitcase, and I met him on the water front.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Strange man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And he took, immediately-- the first thing he wanted was my 2,000 guilders.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And then he carried my suitcase.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And as we were walking toward the Grand Central Station, where we were supposed to take the train, it occurred to me, a few days ago, I didn't know this man.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I didn't even know that he existed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And now, this man was carrying my suitcase, was carrying my money, was carrying my life in his hands.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And then we went to the station, and there was a group of other people who-- this station was crazy.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Everybody was trying to get out of Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "It was really, absolutely wild.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
